$lang['What is the difference between a Hexadecimal and a Decimal?'] = 'Apa bedane antarane Hexadecimal lan Decimal?';
$lang['The hexadecimal system is a base 16 number notation, while the decimal system is a base 10 number notation. In other words, the hexadecimal system uses 16 symbols to represent numbers, while the decimal system uses 10 symbols. This expansion also allows for a higher information density-hexadecimal digits can represent twice as many values as decimal digits.'] = 'Sistem heksadesimal minangka notasi angka 16 basis, dene sistem desimal minangka notasi angka 10 basis. Ing tembung liya, sistem heksadesimal nggunakake 16 simbol kanggo makili angka, dene sistem desimal nggunakake 10 simbol. Ekspansi iki uga ngidini kanggo informasi sing luwih dhuwur kapadhetan-heksadesimal digit bisa makili kaping pindho minangka akeh angka minangka digit desimal.';
$lang['Hexadecimal numbers are made up of 16 digits instead of the 10 in a decimal number. The order of these numbers starts over after F (or 15 in decimal), while it doesn’t in the decimals. Check out the table below to see how they compare!'] = 'Nomer heksadesimal dumadi saka 16 digit tinimbang 10 ing angka desimal. Urutan nomer kasebut diwiwiti sawise F (utawa 15 ing desimal), nalika ora ana ing desimal. Priksa tabel ing ngisor iki kanggo ndeleng carane mbandhingake!';
$lang['How do you convert a Hexadecimal to a Decimal?'] = 'Kepiye cara ngowahi heksadesimal dadi desimal?';
$lang['When converting hexadecimal to decimal, the first step is to divide the hex number by 16. This will give you the base number. The second step is to divide each digit of the hex number by 16 and write down the results. Finally, add up all of the numbers that were just calculated.'] = 'Nalika ngowahi heksadesimal dadi desimal, langkah pisanan yaiku dibagi nomer hex kanthi 16. Iki bakal menehi nomer dhasar. Langkah kapindho yaiku dibagi saben digit nomer hex kanthi 16 lan nulis asile. Pungkasan, tambahake kabeh nomer sing diwilang.';
$lang['For example, if someone wants to convert 9F7A to decimal, they would first divide 9F7A by 16 which equals 6051. Then they would divide each digit of 6051 by 16 which equals 381. Lastly, they would add up 381 + 381 + 381 which equals 1144. Therefore, 9F7A in decimal is equal to 1144'] = 'Contone, yen ana wong sing pengin ngowahi 9F7A dadi desimal, dheweke bakal mbagi 9F7A kanthi 16 sing padha karo 6051. Banjur bakal dibagi saben digit 6051 karo 16 sing padha karo 381. Pungkasan, bakal ditambahake 381 + 381 + 381 sing padha. 1144. Mulane, 9F7A ing desimal padha karo 1144';
$lang['How do you convert a Decimal to a Hexadecimal?'] = 'Kepiye carane sampeyan ngowahi desimal dadi heksadesimal?';
$lang['Converting decimal to hexadecimal is a simple process, and can be done with a calculator or online converter. In order to convert the number, divide it by 16 and take the remainder. This remainder will then correspond to a hexadecimal digit. For example, if you have the decimal number 234, divide it by 16 and take the remainder: 234 / 16 = 14 R 2. Therefore, in hexadecimal notation, this number would be written as “E2”.'] = 'Ngonversi desimal dadi heksadesimal minangka proses sing gampang, lan bisa ditindakake kanthi kalkulator utawa konverter online. Kanggo ngowahi nomer, dibagi karo 16 lan njupuk liyane. Sisa iki bakal cocog karo digit heksadesimal. Contone, yen sampeyan duwe nomer desimal 234, dibagi karo 16 lan njupuk sisa: 234 / 16 = 14 R 2. Mulane, ing notasi heksadesimal, nomer iki bakal ditulis minangka &quot;E2&quot;.';
$lang['There are many tools available online that can help with converting between decimal and hexadecimal numbers. Additionally, most calculators have a built-in function that will allow you to do this conversion very easily. With just a few clicks of the mouse or taps on the keyboard, you’ll be able to change any decimal value into its corresponding hexadecimal equivalent!'] = 'Ana akeh alat kasedhiya online sing bisa bantuan karo Ngonversi antarane nomer desimal lan heksadesimal. Kajaba iku, umume kalkulator duwe fungsi sing dibangun sing ngidini sampeyan nindakake konversi iki kanthi gampang. Kanthi mung sawetara klik mouse utawa nutul ing keyboard, sampeyan bakal bisa ngganti sembarang nilai desimal menyang setara heksadesimal sing cocog!';
$lang['What are the benefits of using a Hexadecimal over a Decimal?'] = 'Apa keuntungan nggunakake Heksadesimal tinimbang Decimal?';
$lang['The hexadecimal, or base-16, system was designed to emulate some of the same properties as the decimal system. In other words, it was created to make things easier for us humans. The number 423 has 16 digits instead of 10 digits available in a decimal system. This is because hexadecimal uses a base of 16 symbols instead of 10. After F, the order begins again with 0 and so on and so forth until we get to 15 which is notated as F.'] = 'Sistem heksadesimal, utawa basa-16, dirancang kanggo niru sawetara sifat sing padha karo sistem desimal. Ing tembung liyane, iku digawe kanggo nggawe luwih gampang kanggo kita manungsa. Nomer 423 nduweni 16 digit tinimbang 10 digit sing kasedhiya ing sistem desimal. Iki amarga heksadesimal nggunakake basis 16 simbol tinimbang 10. Sawise F, urutan diwiwiti maneh karo 0 lan sateruse nganti tekan 15 sing dicathet minangka F.';
$lang['Hexadecimal encoding reduces the number of digits by a factor of eight when compared to the decimal system. Additionally, hexadecimal numbers have an information density that is twice as high as decimal numbers do. So, why should you bother learning this funky little numbering scheme? Because it can make your life easier! When working with digital systems or data transmission, using hex will save you time and energy when decoding cryptic messages or data streams.'] = 'Encoding heksadesimal nyuda jumlah digit kanthi faktor wolung yen dibandhingake karo sistem desimal. Kajaba iku, nomer heksadesimal duwe kapadhetan informasi sing kaping pindho luwih dhuwur tinimbang nomer desimal. Dadi, kenapa sampeyan kudu repot sinau skema penomoran cilik sing lucu iki? Amarga bisa nggawe urip luwih gampang! Nalika nggarap sistem digital utawa transmisi data, nggunakake hex bakal ngirit wektu lan energi nalika dekoding pesen samar utawa aliran data.';
$lang['What are the benefits of using a Decimal over a Hexadecimal?'] = 'Apa keuntungan nggunakake Decimal tinimbang Hexadecimal?';
$lang['When it comes to binary coding, Hexadecimal is more efficient because it reduces 8 digits to 2. Additionally, Hex provides a greater degree of information density and higher accuracy in numbers than binary does. This is due to the fact that Hex uses 16 symbols instead of just two like binary. Because of this increased efficiency, Hexadecimal is often used when binary coding in computing and digital electronics as well as for computer science applications.'] = 'Nalika nerangake kode binar, Hexadecimal luwih efisien amarga nyuda 8 digit dadi 2. Kajaba iku, Hex nyedhiyakake tingkat kapadhetan informasi sing luwih dhuwur lan akurasi angka sing luwih dhuwur tinimbang binar. Iki amarga kasunyatan sing Hex nggunakake 16 simbol tinimbang mung loro kaya binar. Amarga efisiensi tambah iki, Heksadesimal asring digunakake nalika coding biner ing komputasi lan elektronik digital uga kanggo aplikasi ilmu komputer.';
$lang['In addition, Hexadecimal takes up less space than decimal. With only two digits instead of 8 binary digits, Hex numbers represent large numbers much more concisely. This can be very helpful when working with computer systems, as there is less chance for mistakes when typing in hex codes compared to decimal codes which have so many decimal points all over the place!'] = 'Kajaba iku, Hexadecimal njupuk spasi kurang saka desimal. Kanthi mung rong digit tinimbang 8 digit binar, nomer Hex makili nomer akeh luwih concisely. Iki bisa banget mbiyantu nalika nggarap sistem komputer, amarga ana kurang kasempatan kanggo kesalahan nalika ngetik kode hex dibandhingake kode desimal kang wis dadi akeh titik desimal ing kabeh panggonan!';
$lang['What is the range of values that can be represented by a Hexadecimal?'] = 'Apa sawetara nilai sing bisa diwakili dening Heksadesimal?';
$lang['A hexadecimal number is a number that uses 16 digits instead of the 10 digits we use in the decimal system. This number system is called base-16, and it helps us to emulate the properties of our familiar decimal system. In hexadecimal, each digit represents a power of 16. The numbers 0 through 9 represent the powers of 1 through 10, while A through F represent the powers of 11 through 15.'] = 'Nomer heksadesimal yaiku angka sing nggunakake 16 digit tinimbang 10 digit sing digunakake ing sistem desimal. Sistem nomer iki diarani basis-16, lan mbantu kita niru sifat sistem desimal sing wis dikenal. Ing heksadesimal, saben digit nggambarake kekuwatan 16. Angka 0 nganti 9 nuduhake kekuwatan 1 nganti 10, dene A nganti F nuduhake kekuwatan 11 nganti 15.';
$lang['Just like in decimal, after 16 symbols have been used in Hexadecimal, the order of numbers starts over again at zero. So, hexadecimal 10 is equal to decimal 16, and hexadecimal 11 is equal to decimal 17. And so on!'] = 'Kaya desimal, sawise 16 simbol digunakake ing Hexadecimal, urutan nomer diwiwiti maneh ing nol. Dadi, heksadesimal 10 padha karo desimal 16, lan heksadesimal 11 padha karo desimal 17. Lan sateruse!';
$lang['What is the range of values that can be represented by a Decimal?'] = 'Apa sawetara nilai sing bisa diwakili dening Decimal?';
$lang['The Decimal system starts with 10 and goes up to 15. This means that the range of values that can be represented by a decimal number is from 0-9, followed by A-F (10-15).'] = 'Sistem Decimal wiwit karo 10 lan dadi nganti 15. Iki tegese sawetara nilai sing bisa dituduhake dening nomer desimal saka 0-9, ngiring dening AF (10-15).';
$lang['How do you decode Hexadecimal?'] = 'Kepiye cara decode Hexadecimal?';
$lang['When it comes to decoding Hexadecimal, there are a few things you need to know. First, just like the decimal system, the hexadecimal system has 10 symbols (0-9) that represent numbers. However, in hexadecimal, these digits have values that are twice as large as their counterparts in the decimal system. So, while the number “10” is represented by the symbol “A” in hexadecimal, it would be equal to “10” in the decimal system.'] = 'Nalika nerangake dekoding Heksadesimal, ana sawetara perkara sing sampeyan kudu ngerti. Kaping pisanan, kaya sistem desimal, sistem heksadesimal nduweni 10 simbol (0-9) sing makili angka. Nanging, ing heksadesimal, angka-angka kasebut nduweni nilai sing kaping pindho luwih gedhe tinimbang pasangan ing sistem desimal. Dadi, nalika angka &quot;10&quot; diwakili dening simbol &quot;A&quot; ing heksadesimal, bakal padha karo &quot;10&quot; ing sistem desimal.';
$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'Kajaba iku, sawise tekan 9 ing Hexadecimal (diwakili dening &quot;F&quot;), kita wiwit ngetung maneh ing 10 (&quot;10&quot;). Pola iki terus nganti tekan 15 (&quot;1F&quot;), ing wektu iku kita ngreset maneh menyang 0 lan wiwit ngetang maneh ing 16 (&quot;20&quot;). Iki bisa uga katon mbingungake ing wiwitan, nanging kanthi latihan sethithik, bakal dadi alam liya!';
$lang['Lastly, just like in base 10 (the decimal system), each place value of a hexadecimal number represents a power of 16. So for example, if we had the number 423004 stored as a hexadecimal value:'] = 'Pungkasan, kaya ing basis 10 (sistem desimal), saben nilai panggonan saka nomer heksadesimal nggambarake daya 16. Dadi contone, yen kita duwe nomer 423004 sing disimpen minangka nilai heksadesimal:';
$lang['The 4 would represent 400 (4×100), 2 would represent 20 (2×10), 3 would represent 3 (3×1), and the 0 would represent 0 (0x0).'] = '4 makili 400 (4×100), 2 makili 20 (2×10), 3 makili 3 (3×1), lan 0 makili 0 (0x0).';
$lang['This is just a basic overview of decoding Hexadecimal numbers. If you’re looking for more detailed information, there are plenty of online resources that can help!'] = 'Iki mung ringkesan dhasar saka dekoding angka Heksadesimal. Yen sampeyan nggoleki informasi sing luwih rinci, ana akeh sumber online sing bisa mbantu!';
